# llm/

LLM-specific guidelines and templates for Intent projects. Contains the module registry (Highlander Rule enforcer), decision trees for code placement, agent documentation, code archetypes, and template files for project-specific guidance.

## Files

- `MODULES.md` -- Module registry enforcing the Highlander Rule (one module per concern)
- `DECISION_TREE.md` -- Decision tree for determining where code should live (which module/layer)
- `AGENTS.md` -- Intent agent system documentation; available agents and their specialties
- `ARCHETYPES.md` -- Code templates for Elixir/Phoenix (services, controllers, LiveViews, etc.)
- `_CLAUDE.md` -- Template for project-specific CLAUDE.md guidelines (project-level rules and structure)
- `_DEPENDENCY_GRAPH.md` -- Template for app-level dependency rules in umbrella applications
- `_llm_preamble.md` -- Template for LLM session preamble; baseline context for new sessions
